Module to compute physical properties of liquid water.

Functions

density([T])

Provides density of liquid water at a temperature T.

Provides heat of vaporization of liquid water at a temperature T.

prandtlnumber([T])

Provides Prandtl number of liquid water at a temperature T

specificheat([T])

Provides specific heat of liquid water at a temperature T.

thermalconductivity([T])

Provides thermal conductivity of liquid water at a temperature T.

viscosity([T])

Provides viscosity of liquid water at a temperature T.

volumeexpansioncoefficient([T])

Provides volume expansion coefficient of liquid water at a temperature T
